<h2>Completing tutor assessment</h2>
<p>To become one of our tutors you'll need to demonstrate you can use our application and leave feedback to the standard required. You'll be able to watch a demonstration of our marking application, and will have as long as you like to use the application before submitting your example feedback.</p>
<p>Once your feedback has been reviewed, we'll activate your account and you can get started immediately. We normally review feedback on the same day you submit it.</p>
	